Name: InnoEdu
About the game: This application allows users to explore the VR Chemistry lab to view molecules and their information. The molecules are extremely tiny and now with VR you can directly grasp and understand more information in an intuitive and interesting way. Help users not need to spend too much time and money to build a lab, instead use Virtual Reality Technology to help users experience remotely.
